    <item>
      <title>外资持股比例上限取消后快乐蜂股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/jollibee-shares-jump-after-foreign-ownership-limit-scrapped</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾最大的餐饮运营商快乐蜂食品公司 (Jollibee Foods Corp.) 的股价周四创下四年多来的最大涨幅，此前该公司获得证券交易所的批准，取消了 40% 的外资持股比例上限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/jollibee-shares-jump-after-foreign-ownership-limit-scrapped</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 03:16:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
